data.description: Motivated Sellers! This cute little house is a wonderful opportunity to enjoy comfortable living with the potential to add your personal touch. The driveway provides off-street parking and a detached garage. The home is conveniently situated, with shopping and other amenities close by. Schedule a showing today and experience the warmth and charm of this semi-updated home! Attached style duplex - only right side is for sale.
